{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":869,"text":"Four years ago,"},{"time":2620,"text":"a security researcher,"},{"time":4422,"text":"or, as most people would call it, a hacker,"},{"time":8671,"text":"found a way to literally"},{"time":10838,"text":"make ATMs throw money at him."},{"time":14041,"text":"His name was Barnaby Jack,"},{"time":17382,"text":"and this technique was later called \"jackpotting\""},{"time":21041,"text":"in his honor."}]},{"cues":[{"time":22950,"text":"I'm here today because I think"},{"time":24799,"text":"we actually need hackers."},{"time":27850,"text":"Barnaby Jack"},{"time":29712,"text":"could have easily turned"},{"time":31199,"text":"into a career criminal or James Bond villain"},{"time":35397,"text":"with his knowledge,"},{"time":36893,"text":"but he chose to show the world"},{"time":39381,"text":"his research instead."},{"time":42070,"text":"He believed that sometimes"},{"time":43923,"text":"you have to demo a threat"},{"time":45963,"text":"to spark a solution."},{"time":48880,"text":"And I feel the same way."},{"time":50810,"text":"That's why I'm here today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":52660,"text":"We are often terrified and fascinated"},{"time":55938,"text":"by the power hackers now have."},{"time":59399,"text":"They scare us."},{"time":61131,"text":"But the choices they make"},{"time":63116,"text":"have dramatic outcomes"},{"time":65286,"text":"that influence us all."},{"time":68274,"text":"So I am here today because I think we need hackers,"},{"time":71609,"text":"and in fact, they just might be"},{"time":75192,"text":"the immune system for the information age."},{"time":79532,"text":"Sometimes they make us sick,"},{"time":81565,"text":"but they also find those hidden threats"},{"time":84920,"text":"in our world,"},{"time":86244,"text":"and they make us fix it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":89089,"text":"I knew that I might get hacked"},{"time":91447,"text":"for giving this talk,"},{"time":93855,"text":"so let me save you the effort."},{"time":96328,"text":"In true TED fashion,"},{"time":98162,"text":"here is my most embarrassing picture."},{"time":102135,"text":"But it would be difficult for you to find me in it,"},{"time":105005,"text":"because I'm the one who looks like a boy"},{"time":108743,"text":"standing to the side."},{"time":110548,"text":"I was such a nerd back then"},{"time":112930,"text":"that even the boys on the\nDungeons and Dragons team"},{"time":115532,"text":"wouldn't let me join."},{"time":117729,"text":"This is who I was,"},{"time":119714,"text":"but this is who I wanted to be:"},{"time":123829,"text":"Angelina Jolie."},{"time":125727,"text":"She portrayed Acid Burn"},{"time":127282,"text":"in the '95 film \"Hackers.\""},{"time":129776,"text":"She was pretty and she could rollerblade,"},{"time":132954,"text":"but being a hacker, that made her powerful."},{"time":137063,"text":"And I wanted to be just like her,"},{"time":139523,"text":"so I started spending a lot of time"},{"time":141889,"text":"on hacker chat rooms and online forums."},{"time":144774,"text":"I remember one late night"},{"time":147107,"text":"I found a bit of PHP code."},{"time":149368,"text":"I didn't really know what it did,"},{"time":150990,"text":"but I copy-pasted it"},{"time":152615,"text":"and used it anyway"},{"time":154329,"text":"to get into a password-protected site"},{"time":156802,"text":"like that."},{"time":158606,"text":"Open Sesame."},{"time":160009,"text":"It was a simple trick,"},{"time":161531,"text":"and I was just a script kiddie back then,"},{"time":164536,"text":"but to me, that trick,"},{"time":165974,"text":"it felt like this,"},{"time":168189,"text":"like I had discovered limitless potential"},{"time":170633,"text":"at my fingertips."},{"time":172424,"text":"This is the rush of power that hackers feel."},{"time":175733,"text":"It's geeks just like me"},{"time":178637,"text":"discovering they have access to superpower,"},{"time":181869,"text":"one that requires the skill and tenacity"},{"time":184496,"text":"of their intellect,"},{"time":186004,"text":"but thankfully no radioactive spiders."}]},{"cues":[{"time":189565,"text":"But with great power"},{"time":191406,"text":"comes great responsibility,"},{"time":193710,"text":"and you all like to think that if we had such powers,"},{"time":197374,"text":"we would only use them for good."},{"time":199653,"text":"But what if you could read your ex's emails,"},{"time":203000,"text":"or add a couple zeros to your bank account."},{"time":206112,"text":"What would you do then?"},{"time":208132,"text":"Indeed, many hackers do not resist"},{"time":210369,"text":"those temptations,"},{"time":212357,"text":"and so they are responsible in one way or another"},{"time":215482,"text":"to billions of dollars lost each year"},{"time":217886,"text":"to fraud, malware or plain old identity theft,"},{"time":221147,"text":"which is a serious issue."},{"time":223025,"text":"But there are other hackers,"},{"time":225010,"text":"hackers who just like to break things,"},{"time":227772,"text":"and it is precisely those hackers"},{"time":230480,"text":"that can find the weaker elements in our world"},{"time":233773,"text":"and make us fix it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":235450,"text":"This is what happened last year"},{"time":237370,"text":"when another security researcher"},{"time":239379,"text":"called Kyle Lovett"},{"time":240944,"text":"discovered a gaping hole"},{"time":242501,"text":"in the design of certain wireless routers"},{"time":245461,"text":"like you might have in your home or office."},{"time":248000,"text":"He learned that anyone could remotely connect"},{"time":250645,"text":"to these devices over the Internet"},{"time":252967,"text":"and download documents from hard drives"},{"time":255728,"text":"attached to those routers,"},{"time":257903,"text":"no password needed."},{"time":259750,"text":"He reported it to the company, of course,"},{"time":262087,"text":"but they ignored his report."},{"time":264401,"text":"Perhaps they thought universal access"},{"time":266265,"text":"was a feature, not a bug,"},{"time":269250,"text":"until two months ago"},{"time":271105,"text":"when a group of hackers used it"},{"time":272538,"text":"to get into people's files."},{"time":274992,"text":"But they didn't steal anything."},{"time":277393,"text":"They left a note:"},{"time":279410,"text":"Your router and your documents"},{"time":281288,"text":"can be accessed by anyone in the world."},{"time":283447,"text":"Here's what you should do to fix it."},{"time":285715,"text":"We hope we helped."},{"time":288093,"text":"By getting into people's files like that,"},{"time":290623,"text":"yeah, they broke the law,"},{"time":292083,"text":"but they also forced that company"},{"time":294551,"text":"to fix their product."}]},{"cues":[{"time":296532,"text":"Making vulnerabilities known to the public"},{"time":298700,"text":"is a practice called full disclosure"},{"time":301445,"text":"in the hacker community,"},{"time":303047,"text":"and it is controversial,"},{"time":305081,"text":"but it does make me think of how hackers"},{"time":307613,"text":"have an evolving effect on technologies we use"},{"time":310599,"text":"every day."},{"time":312095,"text":"This is what Khalil did."},{"time":314373,"text":"Khalil is a Palestinian hacker from the West Bank,"},{"time":316988,"text":"and he found a serious privacy flaw on Facebook"},{"time":320997,"text":"which he attempted to report"},{"time":322847,"text":"through the company's bug bounty program."},{"time":325837,"text":"These are usually great arrangements for companies"},{"time":328494,"text":"to reward hackers disclosing vulnerabilities"},{"time":331671,"text":"they find in their code."},{"time":333360,"text":"Unfortunately, due to some miscommunications,"},{"time":336910,"text":"his report was not acknowledged."},{"time":339946,"text":"Frustrated with the exchange,"},{"time":341791,"text":"he took to use his own discovery"},{"time":345068,"text":"to post on Mark Zuckerberg's wall."},{"time":348203,"text":"This got their attention, all right,"},{"time":350970,"text":"and they fixed the bug,"},{"time":354265,"text":"but because he hadn't reported it properly,"},{"time":357120,"text":"he was denied the bounty usually paid out"},{"time":359345,"text":"for such discoveries."},{"time":361349,"text":"Thankfully for Khalil,"},{"time":363338,"text":"a group of hackers were watching out for him."},{"time":366224,"text":"In fact, they raised more than 13,000 dollars"},{"time":370033,"text":"to reward him for this discovery,"},{"time":372111,"text":"raising a vital discussion in the technology industry"},{"time":375311,"text":"about how we come up with incentives"},{"time":378370,"text":"for hackers to do the right thing."},{"time":380960,"text":"But I think there's a greater story here still."},{"time":383980,"text":"Even companies founded by hackers,"},{"time":386915,"text":"like Facebook was,"},{"time":389302,"text":"still have a complicated relationship"},{"time":391885,"text":"when it comes to hackers."},{"time":393689,"text":"And so for more conservative organizations,"},{"time":396520,"text":"it is going to take time and adapting"},{"time":400038,"text":"in order to embrace hacker culture"},{"time":402620,"text":"and the creative chaos that it brings with it."},{"time":405741,"text":"But I think it's worth the effort,"},{"time":408183,"text":"because the alternative,"},{"time":410163,"text":"to blindly fight all hackers,"},{"time":413993,"text":"is to go against the power you cannot control"},{"time":416581,"text":"at the cost of stifling innovation"},{"time":419882,"text":"and regulating knowledge."},{"time":422076,"text":"These are things that will come back and bite you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":426370,"text":"It is even more true"},{"time":427848,"text":"if we go after hackers"},{"time":429927,"text":"that are willing to risk their own freedom"},{"time":432964,"text":"for ideals like the freedom of the web,"},{"time":435867,"text":"especially in times like this, like today even,"},{"time":439930,"text":"as governments and corporates"},{"time":442550,"text":"fight to control the Internet."},{"time":445776,"text":"I find it astounding"},{"time":448100,"text":"that someone from the shadowy\ncorners of cyberspace"},{"time":451113,"text":"can become its voice of opposition,"},{"time":453928,"text":"its last line of defense even,"},{"time":456570,"text":"perhaps someone like Anonymous,"},{"time":459987,"text":"the leading brand of global hacktivism."},{"time":463840,"text":"This universal hacker movement"},{"time":466100,"text":"needs no introduction today,"},{"time":467706,"text":"but six years ago"},{"time":469809,"text":"they were not much more than an Internet subculture"},{"time":473238,"text":"dedicated to sharing silly pictures of funny cats"},{"time":476157,"text":"and Internet trolling campaigns."},{"time":479587,"text":"Their moment of transformation was in early 2008"},{"time":484429,"text":"when the Church of Scientology"},{"time":486079,"text":"attempted to remove certain leaked videos"},{"time":489146,"text":"from appearing on certain websites."},{"time":493549,"text":"This is when Anonymous was forged"},{"time":495989,"text":"out of the seemingly random collection"},{"time":498620,"text":"of Internet dwellers."},{"time":500363,"text":"It turns out,"},{"time":502817,"text":"the Internet doesn't like it"},{"time":504146,"text":"when you try to remove things from it,"},{"time":506769,"text":"and it will react with cyberattacks"},{"time":509739,"text":"and elaborate pranks"},{"time":511840,"text":"and with a series of organized protests"},{"time":514489,"text":"all around the world,"},{"time":515834,"text":"from my hometown of Tel Aviv"},{"time":517822,"text":"to Adelaide, Australia."},{"time":520066,"text":"This proved that Anonymous and this idea"},{"time":523196,"text":"can rally the masses from the keyboards"},{"time":526279,"text":"to the streets,"},{"time":527855,"text":"and it laid the foundations"},{"time":529802,"text":"for dozens of future operations"},{"time":532020,"text":"against perceived injustices"},{"time":533960,"text":"to their online and offline world."},{"time":537316,"text":"Since then, they've gone after many targets."},{"time":539341,"text":"They've uncovered corruption, abuse."},{"time":542130,"text":"They've hacked popes and politicians,"},{"time":544950,"text":"and I think their effect is larger"},{"time":546627,"text":"than simple denial of service attacks"},{"time":549424,"text":"that take down websites"},{"time":550800,"text":"or even leak sensitive documents."},{"time":554438,"text":"I think that, like Robin Hood,"},{"time":557480,"text":"they are in the business of redistribution,"},{"time":561380,"text":"but what they are after isn't your money."},{"time":564112,"text":"It's not your documents. It's your attention."},{"time":568842,"text":"They grab the spotlight for causes they support,"},{"time":573382,"text":"forcing us to take note,"},{"time":576013,"text":"acting as a global magnifying glass"},{"time":578478,"text":"for issues that we are not as aware of"},{"time":580622,"text":"but perhaps we should be."},{"time":582731,"text":"They have been called many names"},{"time":584584,"text":"from criminals to terrorists,"},{"time":586355,"text":"and I cannot justify their illegal means,"},{"time":589801,"text":"but the ideas they fight for"},{"time":591942,"text":"are ones that matter to us all."},{"time":595968,"text":"The reality is,"},{"time":597951,"text":"hackers can do a lot more than break things."},{"time":600756,"text":"They can bring people together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":603229,"text":"And if the Internet doesn't like it"},{"time":605552,"text":"when you try to remove things from it,"},{"time":608199,"text":"just watch what happens"},{"time":609100,"text":"when you try to shut the Internet down."},{"time":611929,"text":"This took place in Egypt in January 2011,"},{"time":616521,"text":"and as President Hosni Mubarak"},{"time":619737,"text":"attempted a desperate move"},{"time":621791,"text":"to quash the rising revolution on the streets of Cairo,"},{"time":625633,"text":"he sent his personal troops"},{"time":627503,"text":"down to Egypt's Internet service providers"},{"time":631146,"text":"and had them physically kill the switch"},{"time":633617,"text":"on the country's connection to the world overnight."},{"time":637862,"text":"For a government to do a thing like that"},{"time":639477,"text":"was unprecedented,"},{"time":641196,"text":"and for hackers, it made it personal."},{"time":644660,"text":"Hackers like the Telecomix group"},{"time":646748,"text":"were already active on the ground,"},{"time":648621,"text":"helping Egyptians bypass censorship"},{"time":651439,"text":"using clever workarounds like Morse code"},{"time":653929,"text":"and ham radio."},{"time":655957,"text":"It was high season for low tech,"},{"time":658086,"text":"which the government couldn't block,"},{"time":660650,"text":"but when the Net went completely down,"},{"time":663892,"text":"Telecomix brought in the big guns."},{"time":666830,"text":"They found European service providers"},{"time":669001,"text":"that still had 20-year-old"},{"time":671310,"text":"analog dial-up access infrastructure."},{"time":673890,"text":"They opened up 300 of those lines"},{"time":677292,"text":"for Egyptians to use,"},{"time":679766,"text":"serving slow but sweet Internet connection"},{"time":682603,"text":"for Egyptians."},{"time":684004,"text":"This worked."},{"time":685299,"text":"It worked so well, in fact,"},{"time":687092,"text":"one guy even used it to download an episode"},{"time":689372,"text":"of \"How I Met Your Mother.\""},{"time":693710,"text":"But while Egypt's future is still uncertain,"},{"time":697631,"text":"when the same thing happened in Syria"},{"time":700284,"text":"just one year later,"},{"time":701804,"text":"Telecomix were prepared with those Internet lines,"},{"time":705539,"text":"and Anonymous,"},{"time":706708,"text":"they were perhaps the first international group"},{"time":708954,"text":"to officially denounce the actions"},{"time":710658,"text":"of the Syrian military"},{"time":712571,"text":"by defacing their website."}]},{"cues":[{"time":715375,"text":"But with this sort of power,"},{"time":718867,"text":"it really depends on where you stand,"},{"time":721213,"text":"because one man's hero"},{"time":724722,"text":"can be another's villain,"},{"time":726969,"text":"and so the Syrian Electronic Army"},{"time":729367,"text":"is a pro-Assad group of hackers"},{"time":731838,"text":"who support his contentious regime."},{"time":734503,"text":"They've taken down multiple high-profile targets"},{"time":737185,"text":"in the past few years,"},{"time":738820,"text":"including the Associated Press's Twitter account,"},{"time":742203,"text":"in which they posted a message"},{"time":745219,"text":"about an attack on the White House"},{"time":747375,"text":"injuring President Obama."},{"time":750638,"text":"This tweet was fake, of course,"},{"time":752783,"text":"but the resulting drop in the Dow Jones index"},{"time":755722,"text":"that day was most certainly not,"},{"time":759099,"text":"and a lot of people lost a lot of money."}]},{"cues":[{"time":762361,"text":"This sort of thing is happening\nall over the world right now."},{"time":766267,"text":"In conflicts from the Crimean Peninsula"},{"time":769214,"text":"to Latin America,"},{"time":771576,"text":"from Europe to the United States,"},{"time":773880,"text":"hackers are a force for social,"},{"time":776937,"text":"political and military influence."},{"time":780703,"text":"As individuals or in groups,"},{"time":782954,"text":"volunteers or military conflicts,"},{"time":785594,"text":"there are hackers everywhere."},{"time":788235,"text":"They come from all walks of life,"},{"time":790330,"text":"ethnicities, ideologies and genders, I might add."},{"time":795254,"text":"They are now shaping the world's stage."},{"time":799053,"text":"Hackers represent an exceptional force for change"},{"time":801898,"text":"in the 21st century."},{"time":804062,"text":"This is because access to information"},{"time":806599,"text":"is a critical currency of power,"},{"time":809912,"text":"one which governments would like to control,"},{"time":812878,"text":"a thing they attempt to do by setting up"},{"time":815339,"text":"all-you-can-eat surveillance programs,"},{"time":818999,"text":"a thing they need hackers for, by the way."},{"time":821737,"text":"And so the establishment has long had"},{"time":824384,"text":"a love-hate relationship when it comes to hackers,"},{"time":828091,"text":"because the same people who demonize hacking"},{"time":830849,"text":"also utilize it at large."}]},{"cues":[{"time":835931,"text":"Two years ago,"},{"time":837179,"text":"I saw General Keith Alexander."},{"time":839952,"text":"He's the NSA director and U.S. cyber commander,"},{"time":844170,"text":"but instead of his four star general uniform,"},{"time":847878,"text":"he was wearing jeans and a t-shirt."},{"time":850174,"text":"This was at DEF CON,"},{"time":851918,"text":"the world's largest hacker conference."},{"time":855023,"text":"Perhaps like me, General Alexander"},{"time":856950,"text":"didn't see 12,000 criminals that day in Vegas."},{"time":860770,"text":"I think he saw untapped potential."},{"time":863881,"text":"In fact, he was there to give a hiring pitch."},{"time":867254,"text":"\"In this room right here,\" he said,"},{"time":869894,"text":"\"is the talent our nation needs.\""},{"time":872284,"text":"Well, hackers in the back row replied,"},{"time":875664,"text":"\"Then stop arresting us.\""},{"time":877790,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":881224,"text":"Indeed, for years,"},{"time":883803,"text":"hackers have been on the wrong side of the fence,"},{"time":886619,"text":"but in light of what we know now,"},{"time":889527,"text":"who is more watchful of our online world?"},{"time":893800,"text":"The rules of the game are not that clear anymore,"},{"time":896806,"text":"but hackers are perhaps the only ones"},{"time":900218,"text":"still capable of challenging\noverreaching governments"},{"time":904101,"text":"and data-hoarding corporates"},{"time":906316,"text":"on their own playing field."},{"time":908794,"text":"To me, that represents hope."}]},{"cues":[{"time":911914,"text":"For the past three decades,"},{"time":913238,"text":"hackers have done a lot of things,"},{"time":914789,"text":"but they have also impacted civil liberties,"},{"time":918006,"text":"innovation and Internet freedom,"},{"time":920376,"text":"so I think it's time we take a good look"},{"time":923305,"text":"at how we choose to portray them,"},{"time":925435,"text":"because if we keep expecting\nthem to be the bad guys,"},{"time":929019,"text":"how can they be the heroes too?"},{"time":932489,"text":"My years in the hacker world"},{"time":934500,"text":"have made me realize"},{"time":936142,"text":"both the problem and the beauty about hackers:"},{"time":941875,"text":"They just can't see something broken in the world"},{"time":945033,"text":"and leave it be."},{"time":946680,"text":"They are compelled"},{"time":948360,"text":"to either exploit it or try and change it,"},{"time":951890,"text":"and so they find the vulnerable aspects"},{"time":955806,"text":"in our rapidly changing world."},{"time":957940,"text":"They make us, they force us to fix things"},{"time":962282,"text":"or demand something better,"},{"time":964001,"text":"and I think we need them"},{"time":965995,"text":"to do just that,"},{"time":968201,"text":"because after all, it is not information"},{"time":971470,"text":"that wants to be free, it's us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":974575,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":977937,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":980295,"text":"Hack the planet!"}]}]}